{"rule_id":"RULE-DIST-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"精馏塔回路整体宜保守整定","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"risk_tags":["coupling","process_variation"],"summary":"精馏塔对象通常存在较强耦合、热惯性和工况变化，整定不宜过于激进。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["keep_kp_conservative","limit_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若试投用后振荡放大，优先回退到更保守参数。","operator_note":"先保稳定，再逐步提速。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-DIST-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"关键质量回路优先稳态质量而非极限响应速度","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"quality_related","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["quality_priority"],"summary":"直接影响产品质量的回路应优先抑制振荡和稳态偏差，不应只追求最快跟踪。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","reduce_ki"],"rollback_advice":"质量波动增大时优先降低 Ki。","operator_note":"质量优先于速度。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-TEMP-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"温度回路通常优先 PI 或弱 D 的 PID","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"temperature","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["thermal_inertia","high_noise_risk"],"summary":"温度回路热惯性较强，D 项收益通常有限，噪声大时反而可能恶化控制。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["strong_derivative"],"suggested_actions":["prefer_pi","reduce_kd"],"rollback_advice":"若 MV 抖动明显，优先削弱 D 或改为 PI。","operator_note":"热工回路优先平稳。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
