{"rule_id":"RULE-TEMP-003","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"塔釜温度回路应优先考虑大惯性与大滞后","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"bottom_temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["large_dead_time","thermal_inertia"],"summary":"塔釜温度通常更慢、更滞后，不宜采用激进快速整定。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["increase_closed_loop_time_constant","reduce_kp"],"rollback_advice":"若调节后出现振荡，优先增加闭环时间常数。","operator_note":"塔釜通常慢于塔顶。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-PRES-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"塔压回路宜偏快但不应过冲过大","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"pressure","control_target":"tower_pressure","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["coupling"],"summary":"压力回路通常希望较快响应，但不应因过强比例造成阀门频繁动作。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","gentle_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若出现频繁抖动，优先降低 Kp。","operator_note":"速度重要，但不能牺牲稳定。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"一般流量回路可采用快速 PI，但应明确其过程角色","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["cascade_dependency"],"summary":"流量回路通常是较快对象，但是否能快速整定，取决于其是独立调节回路、串级副环还是质量相关辅助回路。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["allow_higher_kp","watch_master_loop"],"rollback_advice":"若主回路振荡加剧，优先收紧流量子回路。","operator_note":"子回路不能压过主回路。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-DETAIL-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"回流流量回路通常宜快于温度主环，但不宜过度放大塔顶扰动","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"reflux_flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["cascade_dependency","coupling"],"summary":"回流流量常作为塔顶温度串级副环，应比主环快，但若过激进会把塔顶扰动和阀门动作放大。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["strong_derivative","over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","gentle_ki","watch_master_loop"],"rollback_advice":"若塔顶温度波动被放大，优先收紧回流副环。","operator_note":"回流副环要快于主环，但不能抢主环。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-DETAIL-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"回流流量回路与塔顶压力耦合明显时应保守积分","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"reflux_flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["coupling","low_frequency_oscillation"],"summary":"回流流量变化会改变塔顶冷量和分离平衡，积分过强可能形成缓慢振荡。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","LAMBDA"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_integral"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_ki"],"rollback_advice":"出现慢振荡时优先降低 Ki。","operator_note":"回流与塔顶温度、压力强耦合。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-DETAIL-003","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"蒸汽流量副环宜快但不可过冲过大","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"steam_flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["cascade_dependency"],"summary":"蒸汽流量通常作为塔釜温度或热负荷控制的副环，响应宜快，但不应把热负荷波动放大到主环。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","gentle_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若塔釜温度波动增大，优先收紧蒸汽副环。","operator_note":"蒸汽副环可快，但不能抢热平衡主导权。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-DETAIL-004","knowledge_type":"constraint","title":"蒸汽阀存在饱和或卡涩风险时不得继续增强比例","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"steam_flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["saturation","stiction"],"summary":"蒸汽阀门饱和、粘滞或分辨率不足时，提高 Kp 往往只会加剧阀门频繁动作。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","check_valve"],"rollback_advice":"确认阀门问题前不要继续增强参数。","operator_note":"先处理执行器问题，再谈提速。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-DETAIL-005","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"进料流量回路应优先保持物料平衡稳定","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"feed_flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["material_balance"],"summary":"进料流量不仅影响本回路，还直接影响塔内物料和热量平衡，因此整定不宜只追求快。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","LAMBDA"],"discouraged_strategy":["over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","reduce_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若塔内波动被放大，优先收紧进料回路。","operator_note":"进料回路承担全塔平衡入口。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-DETAIL-006","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"冷凝器冷却流量回路整定应避免把压力波动全部压给流量阀","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"flow","control_target":"cooling_flow","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["coupling"],"summary":"冷却流量回路常与塔顶压力强耦合，副环过激进容易引起阀门频繁动作。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","gentle_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若冷端阀门动作频率明显升高，优先降低比例。","operator_note":"冷却流量不能替代压力主调节逻辑。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
