{"rule_id":"RULE-LEVEL-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"液位回路本质上是库存调节，不宜追求过快","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"level","control_target":"level","model_types":["IPDT","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["inventory"],"summary":"液位对象常表现出积分特性，过快整定容易造成进出物流波动放大。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["conservative_pi","PI"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_ki","keep_kp_low"],"rollback_advice":"若上下游波动被放大，进一步减小 Ki。","operator_note":"液位回路先稳库存，再谈速度。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
