{"rule_id":"RULE-MODE-005","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"稳态生产工况是正式整定与参数固化的优先场景","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"scenario_tags":["steady_operation"],"risk_tags":[],"summary":"当物料组成、塔压、回流和热负荷均相对稳定时，辨识结果和整定参数最具代表性。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC","PI"],"discouraged_strategy":[],"suggested_actions":["formal_identification","formal_tuning","persist_experience"],"rollback_advice":"若后续离开稳态工况，应重新评估参数适用性。","operator_note":"稳态工况最适合形成正式结论。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MODE-006","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"原料切换工况下应优先重估对象增益和滞后","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"scenario_tags":["feed_switch"],"risk_tags":["process_variation"],"summary":"原料性质变化会显著影响有效增益、滞后和塔内传热传质分布，原参数往往不再最优。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["reuse_old_parameters_without_check"],"suggested_actions":["reidentify","reduce_aggressiveness"],"rollback_advice":"切换原料后若效果变差，优先回退并重新辨识。","operator_note":"原料变化往往意味着对象变化。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MODE-007","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"塔压波动工况下温度回路整定应额外保守","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"scenario_tags":["tower_pressure_fluctuation"],"risk_tags":["coupling"],"summary":"塔压波动会改变相平衡与温度分布，使温度回路表观动态失真，激进整定更容易放大耦合振荡。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","limit_ki","check_pressure_loop_first"],"rollback_advice":"优先稳住塔压，再评估温度主环。","operator_note":"塔压不稳时，温度结论先保守看待。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MODE-008","knowledge_type":"constraint","title":"回流比大幅调整期间不宜同时强化塔顶温度主环","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"top_temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"scenario_tags":["reflux_adjustment"],"risk_tags":["coupling"],"summary":"回流系统自身正在大幅调节时，塔顶温度主环辨识与整定结论容易受过程过渡态污染。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["wait_until_reflux_stable","reidentify_after_stable"],"rollback_advice":"待回流回路稳定后再调塔顶主环。","operator_note":"回流未稳时不要同时推塔顶主环。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MODE-009","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"蒸汽负荷波动工况下塔釜温度和成分回路应降低激进度","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"bottom_temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"scenario_tags":["steam_fluctuation"],"risk_tags":["coupling","process_variation"],"summary":"蒸汽波动会先扰动塔釜热量平衡，再传导到塔内分离状态，塔釜温度和成分回路不宜维持激进参数。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","slow_down_ki","stabilize_steam_subloop"],"rollback_advice":"优先保障蒸汽流量副环稳定。","operator_note":"热端不稳时，主环参数要收。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MODE-010","knowledge_type":"constraint","title":"分析仪维护或失准工况下成分回路不得据此固化参数","plant_type":"distillation_column","loop_type":"composition","control_target":"composition","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"scenario_tags":["analyzer_maintenance"],"risk_tags":["analyzer_delay"],"summary":"分析仪数据异常会直接污染成分回路的辨识与评估，不能用来形成正式整定结论。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["very_conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["formal_tuning"],"suggested_actions":["temporary_conservative_parameters","disable_experience_persist"],"rollback_advice":"测量恢复前不要固化经验与参数。","operator_note":"测量异常时只能保守运行。","source":"distillation_expert_graph"}
